 Clayton\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Lord\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Lord\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a significant victory\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 100m\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"11.29 seconds\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"her training partner\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"reigning world\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"Under-20\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"champion\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am looking forward to the rest of the season, it has been going great.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have my goals set, and I am just continuing on my journey towards making the Jamaica Olympic team,\\\" said Williams.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1033, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999998396219909, \"rank\": 1.601810251686076e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my goals\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the females, we are working towards our goals and all of us are training and putting in the work, so it is on the day that counts,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our goals\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can not tell until the day, as anything can happen.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always told myself that you just have to go out there, do your best, keep pushing, have faith, put Jesus at the centre of everything you are doing, and keep believing,\\\" Williams asserted.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9415564039082406, \"rank\": 0.0619284795921192, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She holds personal best times of 11.27 in the 100m and 22.88 in the 200m.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"personal best times\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams highlighted that one of her personal goals this year is to improve on her personal best times in both events and therefore, she has been working very hard to meet those targets.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"her personal goals\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"her personal best times\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"both events\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"those targets\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jamaican sprinter Jodean Williams \\\"Of course, I do have certain times that I am targeting because you need to put a time on paper.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1732, \"end\": 1740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9055128148240523, \"rank\": 0.10434655110748266, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"certain times\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have told myself that you need to keep working, and time will come,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams explained that her decision to switch from the Racers track club to SprinTech at the end of last season was very personal, and she hopes it will result in her achieving great things this season.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"the Racers\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"SprinTech\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"last season\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"great things\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, adaptation is not a problem because I enjoy what I do and love what I do.\", \"from\": 2150, \"t